---

<Layout title={title}>
  <Header homepage_path={homepage_path}>
    <Link href="#about_digital" class="nav-link">About</Link>
    <Link href="#programmes" class="nav-link">Programmes</Link>
    <Link href="#registration" class="nav-link btn btn-danger">
      Register Today
    </Link>
  </Header>

  <main class="main">
    {is_thank_you && <slot name="thank-you" />}

    <!-- bg_laptop={bg_laptop} -->
    <SectionMasthead
      bg_mobile={bg_mobile}
      bg_laptop={bg_laptop}
      bg_desktop={bg_desktop}
      bg_img_style="object-position: center;"
    >
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center text-center text-md-start">
          <div class="col-lg-8" style="filter: drop-shadow(2px 4px 8px #0003);">
            <div style="text-shadow: 2px 2px 10px black">
              <h1 class="font-weight-bold mb-4 text-light">
                Unlock your potential <span class="d-block"
                  >with MCKL's international business programmes</span
                >
                <!-- Launch Your Business Career in
                <span class="d-block">IR 4.0 with MCKL</span> -->
              </h1>
              <p class="h4 text-light">
                12-weeks of industrial training for all students.
              </p>
              <p class="h4 text-light">
                Scholarships and financial aid available.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="my-3">
              <a
                class="m-2 btn btn-secondary btn-lg"
                href={`${homepage_path}#programmes_offered`}>Learn More</a
              >
              <a
                class="m-2 btn btn-primary btn-lg"
                href={`${homepage_path}#registration`}>Enquire Now</a
              >
            </div>
            <OpenDayInvitation />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </SectionMasthead>
    <style lang="scss" is:global>
      .masthead__picture {
        @include media-breakpoint-down(md) {
          filter: brightness(1.3) contrast(0.9);
          z-index: -1;
          opacity: 0.5;
        }
        filter: brightness(1.1);
      }
    </style>

    <!-- intro -->
    <section
      class="bg-primary py-4 text-center border-bottom border-secondary text-light text-light__heading"
      style="border-width: 6px !important"
    >
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center text-center">
          <div class="col-lg-7">
            <h3 class="my-4">Why Study Business with MCKL?</h3>
            <p>
              Industrial Revolution 4.0 (IR 4.0) is upon us and has impacted
              societies, business models, future jobs and careers. As more
              emphasis is placed on smart solutions, automation, data analytics
              and internet of things (IoT) technology in businesses, the demand
              for digitally-skilled talents are also widely growing.
            </p>
            <p>
              To meet the demands of IR 4.0, MCKL recognises the need to equip
              our students with future-oriented skills. Our new diploma
              programmes are here to prepare our students to be job-ready!
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div
          class="row row-cols-1 row-cols-sm-2 row-cols-md-3 justify-content-center my-4 text-start"
        >
          {
            card_icons.map((item) => (
              <div class="col mb-4">
                <CardIcon classes="card__icon--business" item={item} />
              </div>
            ))
          }
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- about -->
    <section id="programmes_offered">
      <!-- title -->
      <div class="bg-secondary py-4 text-center">
        <h2 class="text-primary">Programmes Offered</h2>
        <p class="h5 text-primary">Intake: 19 January, 14 June & 23 August 2024</p>
      </div>

      <SectionBusinessProgramme
        featured_img={featured_ddm}
        prog={ddm.frontmatter}
      >
        <div slot="content">
          <h4 class="my-4">What is Digital Marketing?</h4>
          <p>
            Have you ever wondered what goes on behind the scenes of every
            Chinese New Year video or Hari Raya contest that you see online?
            Digital marketing is the combination of various marketing effort
            that takes place online in one form or another. By leveraging
            various digital channels such as search engines, email, social
            media, websites, and mobile apps, brands are able to reach out to
            their target audience much more easily, efficiently as well as
            precisely than ever before. From creating brand awareness to driving
            sales, digital marketing is now where traditional advertising used
            to be.
          </p>
        </div>
        <BsAccordion
          client:idle
          show_first={true}
          accordion_id="ddm"
          accordion_items={[
            { title: "Why study Digital Marketing?" },
            { title: "What happens next after graduation?" },
          ]}
          slot="after_content"
        >
          <div slot="content-0">
            <p>
              Digital marketing has evolved over the years making it one of the
              most sought-after forms of advertising in today's fast-changing
              world. The programme is designed to equip students with in-demand
              digital skills such as search engine optimisation (SEO), search
              engine marketing (SEM), social media marketing, electronic direct
              mail (EDM) marketing and other digital platforms. The programme
              also develops skills that are needed to analyse market needs and
              trends, define target markets and unlock business opportunities in
              a competitive environment.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div slot="content-1">
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-md-6">
                <p>
                  Students are now <strong>job-ready</strong> to explore careers
                  such as:
                </p>
                <ul>
                  <li>Content Creator Digital Marketing</li>
                  <li>Digital Marketing Executive</li>
                  <li>E-Service Executive</li>
                  <li>Market Research Analyst</li>
                  <li>Media Content Strategist</li>
                  <li>Online Business Entrepreneur</li>
                  <li>Social Media Executive</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-6">
                <p>
                  Students can also top up 2 years to progress into a bachelorâ€™s
                  degree programme at our partner universities:
                </p>

                <div class="media align-items-center mb-2">
                  <figure>
                    <img
                      width="96"
                      src={logo_deakin_square}
                      class=""
                      alt="Deakin University, Australia"
                    />
                    <p style="line-height: 1">
                      <small>CRICOS PROVIDER <br />NO. 00113B</small>
                    </p>
                  </figure>
                  <div class="media-body ms-3">
                    <h5 class="mt-0">Deakin University, Australia</h5>
                    <p>Commerce | Business Analytics</p>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div class="media align-items-center mb-2">
                  <img
                    width="96"
                    src={logo_keele_square}
                    class=""
                    alt="Keele University, UK"
                  />
                  <div class="media-body ms-3">
                    <h5 class="mt-0">Keele University, UK</h5>
                    <p>
                      International Business Management | Marketing and Business
                      Management
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div class="media align-items-center mb-2">
                  <img
                    width="96"
                    src={logo_sheffield_square}
                    class=""
                    alt="Sheffield Hallam University, UK"
                  />
                  <div class="media-body ms-3">
                    <h5 class="mt-0">Sheffield Hallam University, UK</h5>
                    <p>
                      Digital Marketing | Business and Digital Technology |
                      Information Technology with Business Studies
