                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </BsAccordion>
      </SectionBusinessProgramme>

      <SectionBusinessProgramme
        featured_img={featured_ddb}
        prog={ddb.frontmatter}
      >
        <div slot="content">
          <h4 class="my-4">What is Digital Business?</h4>
          <p>
            Have you ever wondered how to start your own online business or how
            international brands have embraced Digital Business as part of their
            retail strategy? Digital Business is a sales channel that enables
            entrepreneurs and businesses to sell online, directly to consumers,
            but thatâ€™s not all. It is also about marketing, gaining consumer
            trust and confidence and so much more; without physically
            interacting with customers both locally and beyond geographical
            borders.
          </p>
        </div>
