          slot="after_content"
        >
          <div slot="content-0">
            <p>
              Digital Business has great future prospects as most businesses are
              moving online for greater penetration into the market through
              faster and wider reach via the usage of the Internet. The
              programme will provide students with an in-depth understanding of
              the context, nature, role and significance of e-business / Digital
              Business activities in a dynamic business world. Students will
              gain exposure to theoretical and practical knowledge of conducting
              an online business over the Web and also the fundamentals of
              entrepreneurship for the opportunity to start their own
              businesses.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div slot="content-1">
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-md-6">
                <p>
                  Students are now <strong>job-ready</strong> to explore careers
                  such as:
                </p>
                <ul>
                  <li>Digital Marketing Executive</li>
                  <li>Digital Business Entrepreneur</li>
                  <li>Digital Business Executive</li>
                  <li>Digital Business Planner</li>
                  <li>Market Research Analyst</li>
                  <li>Online Business Analyst</li>
                  <li>Web Development Specialist</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-6">
                <p>
                  Students can also top up 1-2 years to progress into a
                  bachelorâ€™s degree programme at our partner universities:
                </p>

                <div class="media align-items-center mb-2">
                  <figure>
