                      class=""
                      alt="Deakin University, Australia"
                    />
                    <p style="line-height: 1">
                      <small>CRICOS PROVIDER <br />NO. 00113B</small>
                    </p>
                  </figure>
                  <div class="media-body ml-3">
                    <h5 class="mt-0">Deakin University, Australia</h5>
                    <p>Commerce | Business</p>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div class="media align-items-center mb-2">
                  <img
                    width="96"
                    src={logo_keele_square}
                    class=""
                    alt="Keele University, UK"
                  />
                  <div class="media-body ml-3">
                    <h5 class="mt-0">Keele University, UK</h5>
                    <p>
                      International Business Management | Marketing and Business
                      Management
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div class="media align-items-center mb-2">
                  <img
                    width="96"
                    src={logo_middlesex_square}
                    class=""
                    alt="Middlesex University London, UK"
                  />
                  <div class="media-body ml-3">
                    <h5 class="mt-0">Middlesex University London, UK</h5>
                    <p>International Business Administration</p>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <div class="media align-items-center mb-2">
                  <img
                    width="96"
                    src={logo_sheffield_square}
                    class=""
                    alt="Sheffield Hallam University, UK"
                  />
                  <div class="media-body ml-3">
                    <h5 class="mt-0">Sheffield Hallam University, UK</h5>
                    <p>
                      Business and Finance | Business Management | Business and
                      Digital Technology | Information Technology with Business
                      Studies
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </BsAccordion>
      </SectionBusinessProgramme>

      <SectionBusinessProgramme
        featured_img={featured_dft}
        prog={dft.frontmatter}
      >
        <p slot="after_title">
          <small>*Programmes offered in Kuala Lumpur Campus only</small>
        </p>
        <div slot="content">
          <h4 class="my-4">What is Financial Technology (FinTech)?</h4>
          <p>
            Imagine 10 years ago, would you have ever guessed that we are en
            route to becoming a cashless society or that financial instruments
            no longer require banks or face to face interactions to take place?
            This is FinTech. FinTech, or financial technology, is used to
            describe businesses that use technological innovation to enhance or
            automate their financial services and products. This allows for
            quicker processes, personalised services, and more accurate data.
            Technology in finance continues to evolve due to advances in big
            data, artificial intelligence (AI), machine learning and data
            science. FinTech is now being used in various areas of finance such
            as mobile banking, cryptocurrency, blockchain, investment and
            trading.
          </p>
        </div>
        <BsAccordion
          client:idle
          show_first={true}
          accordion_id="dft"
          accordion_items={[
            { title: "Why study Financial Technology (FinTech)?" },
            { title: "What happens next after graduation?" },
          ]}
          slot="after_content"
        >
          <div slot="content-0">
            <p>
              FinTech is a rapidly growing industry and will continue to expand
              for years to come. Talents with cross-discipline knowledge and
              skills in Finance and Information Technology are in demand for the
              coming years. The programme will fully equip students with
              comprehensive knowledge and future-oriented skills in Financial
              Technology. Some of the key areas include Financial Accounting,
              Financial Management, Principles of Investment and Blockchain.
              With a comprehensive programme, MCKL aims to produce future-ready
              students to meet the need of the FinTech industry.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div slot="content-1">
            <div class="row">
              <div class="col-auto">
                <p>
                  Students are now <strong>job-ready</strong> to explore careers
                  such as:
                </p>
                <ul>
                  <li>App Developer</li>
                  <li>Blockchain Developer</li>
                  <li>Cybersecurity Analyst</li>
                  <li>Data Scientist</li>
                  <li>Financial Analyst</li>
                  <li>FinTech Quantitative Developer</li>
                  <li>FinTech Systems Analyst</li>
                  <li>Investment Analyst</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <div class="col-md-6">
                <p>
                  Students can also choose to progress into a <strong
                    >bachelorâ€™s degree</strong
                  >
                  programme at our partner universities.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </BsAccordion>
      </SectionBusinessProgramme>

      <!-- youtube -->
      <section id="youtube" class="my-5 text-center">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-10">
              <h2>MCKL New Business Programmes Webinar</h2>
              <p class="lead">Future Proof with Business & Computing Studies</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="row justify-content-center my-3">
            <div class="col-lg-6">
              <iframe
                class="w-100 border-0"
                style="aspect-ratio: 16 / 9"
                src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/ipQasHCAgDo"></iframe>
            </div><div class="col-lg-6">
              <iframe
                class="w-100 border-0"
                style="aspect-ratio: 16 / 9"
                src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/97JrtA4J-kk"></iframe>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- articles -->
      <SectionProgrammeArticles />

      <!-- partners -->
